import React from 'react'
import * as s from './AddBlogPost.styling'

export const AddBlogPost = () => {
    return (
        <>
            
            <s.AddBlogSection>
                <s.AddBlogWrap>
                    <s.AddBlogPostForm>
                        <s.Header>Blog Post</s.Header>
                        <s.AddBlogSubheading>
                            In thisw secPlease fill in the form below to add a blog post
                        </s.AddBlogSubheading>
                    </s.AddBlogPostForm>
                </s.AddBlogWrap>
            </s.AddBlogSection>
        </>
    )
};
